!borng.response: During Bo 1, Bo has a 25% chance of picking any of four options: slap, side step, grab and do nothing. Slap beats 2 of those options and therefore wins 50% of the time. During Bo 2, Bo has a 50% chance of slapping, 25% chance of sidestep and 25% grab, therefore grab wins against slap 50% of the time, but slap is faster if you get it first
